title: Will Biden’s Dog Get an ‘Indoguration’ Party?
subtitle: Major Biden’s former shelter is celebrating the "first dog" with a virtual party.
author: Nur Ibrahim
vclaim: The Delaware Humane Association dog shelter is celebrating Major’s ascension to first dog ahead of U.S. President Joe Biden's inauguration with a virtual “Indoguration” party and fundraiser on Jan. 17, 2021.
